        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 49. Legs of Sciadocerinae in Baltic amber, showing large bristlelike macrosetae. A, B. Midleg; C, D. hind leg. A. Eosciadocera pauciseta, femur and tibia, AMNH Ba-JVe565. B. Hennigophora robusta, AMNH Ba-JH58. C. Eosciadocera pauciseta, femur, tibia, basitarsomere. D. Hennigophora robusta, entire leg. E. Base of proleg (coxa and base of femur) of Eosciadocera pauciseta, showing position of exposed scraper of the stridulatum." ;
